                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2770" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0193</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9723 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">以创代承：方太茅氏父子的跨代创业历程</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">窦军生，傅颖</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">方太</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">24 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家族企业；代际创业；创业机会；2017百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Family firm; Intergenerational Entrepreneurship; Entrepreneurial opportunity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了茅理翔和茅忠群父子抓住厨房电器商机，创立宁波方太厨具有限公司，并在行业内崛起的跨代创业历程。方太的创立不是普通的代际传承与接班，方太是由第二代与第一代共同创立的崭新企业。20世纪90年代，茅理翔原先创立的点火枪企业因为行业门槛过低而面临经营困境和管理压力，此时父亲茅理翔希望儿子茅忠群回到家族企业，茅忠群的回归伴随三个条件——不再做原有点火枪业务、旧员工一个不用、迁址办新厂。经过父子二人的努力，方太组建了全新的创业团队；二人在去日本考察之后，确定了生产厨房电器的决定，但具体就生产吸油烟机还是微波炉产生了分歧。通过市场调查和分析研究，茅忠群最终说服了父亲茅理翔，将产品定为吸油烟机。方太的产品设计与性能成功打开了国内高端吸油烟机的市场缺口，发掘了高端吸油烟机这一厨房电器商机。21世纪初，方太面临国内外家电巨头进军吸油烟机市场的产品以及价格竞争，方太在茅氏父子的带领下并没有打价格战，而是继续以创新的姿态保持住了高端吸油烟机的市场份额。立稳脚跟后，方太又以创新的方式进行厨房电器的“嵌入化”与“成套化”，甚至连厨房的橱柜也成立了自己的子品牌，后来又相继进入燃气热水器和水槽洗碗机等相关业务，并取得快速发展，成为国内厨电领域的第一品牌和真正领导者。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case tells us a story about the cross-generational entrepreneurship process in which Mao Lixiang and his son Mao Zhongqun seized the business opportunities in the kitchen electrical appliance market and found Ningbo Fotile Kitchenware Co. Ltd. 20 years after the launching, Fotile has become the leading brand in the industry. It is worth pointing out that Fotile is not an outcome of conventional intergenerational succession in the incumbent industry and market. On the contrary, it is a new venture co-founded in the collaboration of the two generations outside of the existing territory. In the 1990s, due to the low threshold to enter the industry and the cut-throat competition, Mao Lixiang’s ignitor business was on the edge of bankruptcy. At that moment, Mao Lixiang hoped that his son Mao Zhongqun would come back to the family business to help him find their own blue ocean. Mao Zhongqun was finally persuaded by his parents to return, but he proposed three preconditions- (1) abandoning the ignitor business; (2) ridding off all the original staff; (3) relocating to the new development zone of the Cixi city. With the efforts of the father and the son, Fotile built a totally new venture team. After a business visit to Japan, the father and the son made a critical decision to produce kitchen appliances although they still had different views about the final product – extractor hood or microwave oven. After a systematic market analysis, Mao Zhongqun finally convinced his father and reached a consensus to focus on extractor hood. The product design and superior performance of Fotile products successfully filled the gaps of lacking domestic high-end extractor hood products, capturing this kitchen appliance business opportunity. At the beginning of the 21st century, Fotile was confronted with the competitions from their domestic and foreign competitors who also started to enter the extractor hood market. In such situation, Fotile continued to keep innovation and defended the high-end extractor hood market share instead of starting or involving a price war. With a firm foothold, Fotile followed its innovative path and moved on to promote the “embedded” “complete set” of kitchen appliances. It has established its own sub-brand in kitchen cabinets. So far, they have had a strong position in many businesses such as gas water heater and sink dishwashers, etc. With the impressive achievement, Fotile has becoming the leader in the domestic kitchen electric field.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业机会的辨识 创业机会的开发 新创企业成长</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
